2. IMPLEMENTATION SUMMARY
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  CallSequenceExtractor:  SequenceItem(serviceName, eventType, detail); encode(itemMap, AtomicInteger);
                          extractFromTraces(events, topology) — group by traceId, ≥2 events, sort by timestamp, classifyEventType, extractDetail;
                          extractFromTemporalWindows(events, windowSize) — sort by timestamp, sliding windows, ≥2 events per window.
  SequencePatternMiner:   mine(sequences, minSupportRatio) — shared encoding (ConcurrentHashMap + AtomicInteger), SPMF format "item -1 ... -2",
                          runPrefixSpan via reflection (AlgoPrefixSpan) when SPMF on classpath; parseOutputLine "#SUP: count"; decode to DiscoveredPattern;
                          classifyPatternType: NORMAL_FLOW, ERROR_PROPAGATION, CASCADE_FAILURE, ASYNC_FANOUT, RETRY_PATTERN (3+ consecutive same item).
  PatternAnalyzer:       analyzePatterns(patterns, topology) → EnrichedPattern(pattern, involvedServices, crossesServiceBoundary, hasErrors, involvesKafka, description);
                          generatePatternDescription "svc::EVENT(detail) → ...".
  PatternMiningService:  minePatterns(snapshotId, events, topology) — extractFromTraces + extractFromTemporalWindows(30s), merge sequences,
                          miner.mine(MIN_SUPPORT 0.03), analyzer.analyzePatterns, minio.putJson evidence/patterns/{snapshotId}.json, metrics flowforge.patterns.discovered/error.
  PatternMiningConfig:   @Bean SequencePatternMiner(minSupport, maxPatternLength) from flowforge.pattern-mining.* properties.

